### 📥 Installation
```bash
# Update to latest version
npm update

# Or install specific version
npm install @[package-name]@[version]
```

### 🧪 Testing the Release
```bash
# Run all tests
npm test

# Run e2e tests
npm run test:e2e

# Run with coverage
npm run test:cov
```
